{
  "texts": [
    "DrCIF replaces both TSF and RISE for the interval and frequency representations.",
    "An ensemble of ROCKET classifiers called the Arsenal is introduced as a new convolutional based approach.",
    "Estimation of test accuracy via cross-validation is replaced by an adapted form of out-of-bag error, although the final model is still built using all training data.",
    "Unlike previous versions, HC2 is capable of classifying multivariate time series.",
    "Figure 35 illustrates the structure of HC2, while Fig. 36 visualises the ensemble members of HIVE-COTE over its evolution."
  ]
}